iragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span><span style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">小型张资料提供：金陵刻经处</span></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span><span style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">责任编辑：王静</span></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span><span style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">印 制 厂：北京邮票厂 </span></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		 \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span><span style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">       玄奘，洛州缑氏（今河南洛阳偃师）人，唐代佛教学者、旅行家、佛经翻译家，法相宗创始人，被尊称为“三藏法师”。他13岁出家，四处求学，因感各类佛典众说纷纭，难有定论，决心西行求法。唐太宗贞观年间，经凉州出玉门关西行抵印度，进入当时印度佛教的中心那烂陀寺学习。后又游学印度各地，与当地学者展开辩论，声名远播。贞观十九年（645年）回到长安，译出经、论75部1335卷，对我国佛教思想的发展影响极大。有记录西行见闻的《大唐西域记》，<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">经典译著《</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/110998.htm\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">大般若经</span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">》、《</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/subview/16004/5395487.htm\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">心经</span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">》等传于后世。</span></span></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span><span style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">       邮票设计以中国画工笔重彩的形式，刻画人物生动细致，画面古朴典雅。小型张以玄奘译著《心经》为背景，与画面容为一体，恰到好处。</span></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		 \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">重要声明：</span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">1、零售邮票以发货实物为准，图片仅供参考。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">2、同一小版商品中如含多个小版时，有可能出现每版编号不同的情况，以此为由申请换货或拒收的将不予处理，由此产生的任何运费由客户自行承担，请熟知后谨慎购买。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">3、购买多套套票类订单，我们会根据中国邮政集团公司的发行要求及加工需要，决定邮票套票的发货形式（是否破版），并保证邮票图案范围内的品相完好，邮票图案外所有区域的任何瑕疵，不属于质量问题，以此为由申请换货或拒收的将不予处理（小版及小本票除外），由此产生的任何运费由客户自行承担，请熟知后谨慎购买。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">4、由于邮票的特殊性，邮票类订单不支持退货退款。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, \'儷黑 Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro He\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\n		<span style=\"co